  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMessageEvent
    Defines an abstract message event, specifically intended for events that trigger on reception of a message, and that are constructed automatically via MessageDispatcher.
    ChatMessageEvent
    Defines a chat message handler.
    LoginMessageEvent
    Defines a login message event.
    RegistrationMessageEvent
    Defines a registration message.
